{"id": "1389423794174693469", "channel_id": "1389423794174693469", "type": 0, "author_id": "1201931373623902288", "author_name": "ichikaguya._52033", "author_bot": false, "content": "莉莉：提供死抗、坦傷害、回血、引爆毒（報償打擊）\n★道中扣0費報償打擊收頭有奇效\n\n熔朵：提供狂氣、回血、易傷虛弱\n★終末後讓普拉狂洗3費疊毒\n\n寧菲：沒什麼特別，就是一個無情的爆毒機器\n\n普拉：提供銀鑰、提供賣卡（很重要，謝謝你拉蒙娜🦸🏻‍♀️）、超限提供雙發銀鑰、狂氣拉牌\n\n銀鑰：虛無瘟疫（超愛用，能回狂又能爆毒。配上超限普拉的雙發銀鑰收頭有奇效）\n\n這隊伍用起來就真的很無腦，基本就是狂氣滿了開，沒了🫴🏻🧠\n遇到開狂會疊臨時瘋狂那顆馬鈴薯🥔會很容易翻車\n這時候莉莉的死抗就是我唯一的信仰🛐\n影片打得很爛，但幸運地信仰檢定有過🎰\n\nhttps://youtu.be/JysnaFrLros?si=Q2VzUOAmn06fWTSH", "timestamp": "2025-07-01T01:54:06.777000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-07-01T03:24:42.051000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}], "attachments": [{"id": "1389423794820743299", "filename": "Screenshot_20250701-023409.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2360398, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1389423794174693469/1389423794820743299/Screenshot_20250701-023409.png?ex=69fb47fe&is=69f9f67e&hm=8212bea0b2679d2c445a766ead7ea38bcb6243ce9dd023507e1446c10d121e2f&"}, {"id": "1389423795265343569", "filename": "Screenshot_20250701-070544.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 242953, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1389423794174693469/1389423795265343569/Screenshot_20250701-070544.png?ex=69fb47ff&is=69f9f67f&hm=f796a41d40289cc4a7013b731c95341fc8ecb51f01a9db6dc28952f5a08471c2&"}], "embeds": [{"type": "video", "title": "【忘卻前夜】星辰篇H2-12 至純混沌中毒隊", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JysnaFrLros", "description": "3:18 莉莉補血高光時刻✨\n這局沒拿到鐳射頷骨QuQ"}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1389423794174693469", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "混沌中毒隊🧪通關H2-12記錄與分享", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1174179700470460447"]}
